title: easyC v4.zip
description:
This is a patch for easyC V4.2.1.9
All credit for the patch goes to Zer01Kurdish
The patch was made because 75$ per software license can add up for a team with little funding, and i wasn't able to find any patches already done. So i figured I'd give back to tpb now that i have one.

To install patch

1) Install easyC v4 using the installer i went ahead and included for convenience, or just download it from the site.
2) Run it once for initialization.
3) Close it and run the patch as admin.
4) Make sure speakers are turned on for some hacker tunes and admire the cool display for a second :3
5) Click patch, then run easyC v4 as admin to pull up the registration window.
6) Go to manual unlock and type in "12345678"
7) You should see that you now have a seven day subscription, and that's all.

Now go code some awesome functions! gl and have fun
